Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:42.74,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.43,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.50,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! It's gone! It's gone! It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.25,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Gone, gone, gone! My thing is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.38,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, #3-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.25,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, #1, this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.26,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0000,0000,0000,,My arms turned into drills!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.22,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0000,0000,0000,,#3-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.53,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,#2... Wait, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:01.40,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.75,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.44,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:10.24,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,The HackaDoll system is full of bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.39,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to this idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.58,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.03,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,We must restore the system!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.05,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! A call at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.02,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,#3, since you're still okay, \Ngo handle it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:23.49,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I'm not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.78,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You look normal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.80,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Mumble, mumble, mumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:28.79,Hackadoll_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:30.79,Hackadoll_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.95,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,Your {\i1}thing{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:33.18,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0000,0000,0000,,There's no{\i1}thing{\i0} there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.09,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}thing{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:36.92,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to stay a girl forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:39.27,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely a {\i1}thing{\i0} of the past now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.80,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway! We must hold out \Nuntil the system is restored!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.95,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:53.51,Hackadoll_Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(256,212)}Episode 6: "A Thing of the Past"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:58.45,Hackadoll_Main,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,Young master, I've brought you some new toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:03.35,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.08,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:10.08,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, synchronizing to you, \Nuh... I'm HackaDoll #3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.41,0:03:14.65,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I came here to advance you... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.74,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:19.73,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I came here to help you \Ndo whatever it is you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.37,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll do anything I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.34,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.10,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Then play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.84,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's all you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.33,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'm totally cool with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.86,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Butler, put her in normal clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:32.46,Hackadoll_Main,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.61,Hackadoll_Main,Maids,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.86,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm totally a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:41.04,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You look... pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.87,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I said you look pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.41,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0000,0000,0000,,I think a flag just went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.70,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.90,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looks like we'll be back to \Nnormal by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:54.96,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0000,0000,0000,,So until then, be a convincing girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.38,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:01.16,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Anything! Anything that's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.03,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.79,recovery_04:27,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Remaining until recovery: 5%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:35.04,sushi,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.04,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.11,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.31,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner isn't ready. Your bath \Nisn't ready. Nothing's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:42.32,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What? What've you been doing all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.28,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.30,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.63,0:04:52.81,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What a hopeless wife you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:56.36,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm a hopeless wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:04:59.55,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Today you're playing with \NMom and Dad all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.97,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,#3, everything's restored here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.07,Hackadoll_Main,#0,0000,0000,0000,,You should return to normal soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.51,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.35,Hackadoll_Main,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,Young master, HackaDoll-san \Nneeds to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.08,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:13.83,Hackadoll_Main,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,No arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.79,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.31,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I played enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.35,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.35,0:05:22.26,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:27.24,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Mom and Dad are always gone, \Nand I don't have any friends at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.80,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.42,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm not lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:37.02,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stay here longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:37.96,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.07,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fun playing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.92,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,It is fun, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.44,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Then live with me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:46.86,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,I know! You should marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:47.82,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.05,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy you anything you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.58,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,So let's live together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:52.45,Hackadoll_Main,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.58,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.62,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.53,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,We're eloping right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.37,Hackadoll_Main,Butler,0000,0000,0000,,Young master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.22,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.15,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.29,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.10,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.60,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.60,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.75,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Because, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.96,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.43,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.60,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.76,Hackadoll_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna leave me all alone, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.27,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:37.79,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.73,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.13,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'm... actually a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.38,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:51.52,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.75,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on to it until we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.34,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.51,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:14.03,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You better not lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.78,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.46,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.46,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.51,Hackadoll_Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
